# Twelve Doors — the mallet: triangle body, a sine octave and a
# twelfth for the metal overtone, envelope snapped fully shut (no
# sustain at all — a strike, not a held tone). Moog ladder, not ARP:
# the ladder's tanh stages saturate on absolute voltage, so it colors
# every hit's passband, not just near cutoff -- the ARP 4072 stays
# clean until the signal is actually near fc, which is too polite here.
waveform 3
osc2_wave 0
osc2_pitch 12
osc2_level 0.35
osc3_wave 0
osc3_pitch 19
osc3_level 0.12
detune 2
sub 0
circuit 0
key_track 0.75
osc_fm 0
sync 0
ring 0
glide 0
pulse_width 0.5
attack 0.001
decay 0.22
sustain 0.0
release 0.12
filter_env 0.6
filter_attack 0.001
filter_decay 0.18
filter_sustain 0.0
filter_release 0.15
cutoff 4200
resonance 0.5
drive 1.9
saturation 1.5
hpf 150
